lead_paragraph: A near-diplomatic incident — as Rio de Janeiro Mayor Eduardo Paes termed it — came to an end on Wednesday ahead of the Olympics.

headline.print_headline: Diplomat Incident Avoided: Aussies Get Rooms at Rio Olympics
